<req/ard-a11y-wcag-baseline> a schema:DigitalDocument ; dcterms:isPartOf <doc/ard#accessibility-req> ; dcterms:title "WCAG 2.2 AA as baseline, not sufficient" ;
    rdf:value "The system shall target WCAG 2.2 AA as a baseline, but compliance shall not be treated as sufficient evidence of zero-input usability." .
